title: Come and rent our expansive three bedroom apartment!
posting_body: ['Get excited about our three bedroom and two bath apartments!', 'It is at an amazing 1741 sq ft.', 'This home has an abundance of space to work with.', ' Plenty of closets and a large kitchen with cupboard space you wouldn’t believe!', 'You will enjoy newly renovated amenities, spacious bedrooms and a spacious living room.', ' Come join our lovely community!!!', 'Convenient and location rich, The Laurel West End offers easy access to downtown less the 8 minutes to Minneapolis via I-494.', 'Part of the highly sought-after West End.', 'Just steps from signature dining, shopping and recreation.', 'These apartments are exceptionally large.', 'If you move into Laurel West End you get to enjoy ideal recreation spaces including an outdoor pool, outdoor kitchen, clubhouse, 24-hour newly renovated fitness center, and a pet friendly facility with a leash-less dog park!', 'Choose from spacious and well-designed floor plans featuring giant bedrooms, full appliance package, open floor plans and large balconies.', 'We invite you to discover exceptional living at The Laurel at the West End.', '-Outdoor Pool', '- Outdoor Kitchen', '- Leash-less dog park', '- Newly renovated fitness center', '-Elevator', '-Large bedrooms', '-Large Closets', '-Energy Efficient Appliances', '-Ceiling Fans in every bedroom!', '- Large Patio/Balcony', '- On-Site Laundry', '-Cable Ready', '-On-Site Management', '-Close to the Twins, Timberwolves & Vikings stadium', '-High Speed Internet Available', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Call or email to schedule a tour today!', '•\tdo NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers']
